a73","tid":2022234,"uid":82070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T08:14:49.000Z","msg":"最近聽到身邊唔少人因為社會發生既事，情緒都受到負面影響<br />\n會覺得好絕望，好傷心，甚至有時夜晚睇睇下會忍唔住喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無巴絲打都有類似經歷？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T08:36:26.000Z","msg":"&quot;你好，這是《自殺．自療．互助舍》。看來你已累積了不少負面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，到我們的網站     <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCi%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=2c35f6e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>     。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》&quot;"},{"pid":"90dc082bae296f655eb7e67c7bb777dda3b32c52","tid":2022234,"uid":82070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eed8f7a425007e166c305af5fb5b9f5fecd7315d","tid":2022234,"uid":80762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T09:58:27.000Z","msg":"聽返啲同香港有關嘅歌，就更加想為香港做到啲嘢<br />\n但身邊嘅同伴幾乎全部都灰心曬，覺得已經冇下一步<br />\n與此同時，負面新聞無停過。唔知可以點<br />\n一回憶到過去就好難平伏心情。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T09:30:02.000Z","msg":"可能有時要比自己空間break下，特別係比情緒可以叉叉電之後再出發"},{"pid":"6e91c1e349e6c48495b9729d4c465ddedd6f36ce","tid":2022234,"uid":82070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e323e0f6661ce62dfcca82183fbf19350c085d3f","tid":2022234,"uid":80762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0db6e393ba7969ba27505f6b7e861dd5c560c62f","tid":2022234,"uid":82070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c690094c2b3c081368b1e8e37b0787bb0e9ccf84","tid":2022234,"uid":80762,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T09:52:37.000Z","msg":"會....負面得好緊要，好無力<br />\n又會回憶過去一年，回憶犧牲的手足，好心痛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T10:03:38.000Z","msg":"個情緒有無影響你其他日常生活?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T10:07:18.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日想喊/夜晚冇人嗰陣唔小心諗返起會真係控制唔到喊，同埋一諗就好頭痛，個人好𢛴又好sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T09:30:50.000Z","msg":"會唔會有時候比自己可以放鬆下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4798cbe6fba3d66ec98a85f8ea04f9cedbd2ea6","tid":2022234,"uid":82070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6917ef774510eceeadd50a48752181310e12ead3","tid":2022234,"uid":200070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T10:27:44.000Z","msg":"會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />學校D counsel 好似藍到黑<br />\n完全唔敢講野比佢地知<br />\n自己一個收收埋埋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:00:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自己一個屈住真係好辛苦<br />\n身邊有無fd support住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b1c64ae14ef67d3973529ebf316b6e81e1745a4","tid":2022234,"uid":82070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb7843ad80a8a3c89ae6bc11caec26cdeafc9adf","tid":2022234,"uid":139256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T10:29:00.000Z","msg":"啱啱去咗睇醫生，佢話我精神太過緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就快頂唔住"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:01:23.000Z","msg":"佢有無比咩意見你?<br />\n路仲有好長，要令自己身體好先再出發!!"},{"pid":"cc3c2e7dcc7a13b8e19fd5f5d68db9722cdd4672","tid":2022234,"uid":82070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26dcdb1efdbc0fd4cb79e09466d64e4065d447ee","tid":2022234,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a52a3a8a10a1991740a84a65c065701724d8ca73","tid":2022234,"uid":82070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T08:14:49.000Z","msg":"最近聽到身邊唔少人因為社會發生既事，情緒都受到負面影響<br />\n會覺得好絕望，好傷心，甚至有時夜晚睇睇下會忍唔住喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無巴絲打都有類似經歷？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T10:33:07.000Z","msg":"握下手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:01:59.000Z","msg":"比個擁抱你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be35f55d9a2a946f078e5df96cccd7d6e31d00fc","tid":2022234,"uid":52705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:03:32.000Z","msg":"去和你SING都已經集唔返氣叫口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5a9cf56ba1ba712344a5997df3d59297a1edd37","tid":2022234,"uid":82070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"779b8426a9931d8f7b66c4ae6064276ff6eb7bd0","tid":2022234,"uid":27910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T10:34:32.000Z","msg":"想死添啦直頭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:04:32.000Z","msg":"仲有好多人同你一齊行緊!!"},{"pid":"4e8f852c0e783f6d01854b6d7d0224e608de6d2a","tid":2022234,"uid":82883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:04:34.000Z","msg":"食隻脆香雞翼調節下心情先啦"},{"pid":"828943dd30bebff2422420745f77a6243099b1ff","tid":2022234,"uid":82070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4b4272cc17dc3bcceeef918bfeeb37a70fba7a7","tid":2022234,"uid":140198,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T17:16:50.000Z","msg":"曾經被影響到內分泌失調，失眠，黎M停唔到，成面爆晒痘，依家好返了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一步真係要戒手機先，唔好比自己接觸過量資訊，或者一感受到情緒唔穩定就即刻放低手機比，自己冷靜返先<br />\n<br />\n唔洗迫得自己太緊，一步一步改善就可以，多啲提醒自己留意情緒，抽離出黎時亦唔好因為咁產生內責感，樓主加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:09:28.000Z","msg":"有時候就係因為自責同內疚感令到好多人唔捨得比自己休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但其實適當的放鬆係好重要， 橡筋拉得太勁都會斷，何況係人既情緒<br />\n每個人盛載情緒容量都唔同，最緊要當feel到自己有唔妥個陣要比自己休息!"},{"pid":"ed8a29ea1469d2a5688a7a44055f560b72f3b044","tid":2022234,"uid":82070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b7ec1e5d8a05adbf75fe94d02c3ea5cfe8c68c9","tid":2022234,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T06:26:14.000Z","msg":"我琴晚自己一個係房睇返啲警暴片，睇完個心情係唔識形容"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:10:56.000Z","msg":"通常夜晚睇完都會好難訓得著..."},{"pid":"13ffe5d5887cca0d2046a010307f3e976d557c1d","tid":2022234,"uid":82070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9209819e0c5a3f80b28475ca1c1d37b7876eafbd","tid":2022234,"uid":29153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T08:09:38.000Z","msg":"無睇好耐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:12:05.000Z","msg":"心情有無好左?"},{"pid":"77ee067f24b22cf5a5b468b66b81f5dcfc27ab17","tid":2022234,"uid":82070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"725379749973b8e2f656ba0f235ed85e38151f5d","tid":2022234,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T08:13:00.000Z","msg":"唔想睇新聞 但身邊有d人好似冇乜感覺 係咪痴線"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:14:07.000Z","msg":"可能只係無表達出自己心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8f95f01ef496291b6c10af491be1ea6c068228f","tid":2022234,"uid":29153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13ffe5d5887cca0d2046a010307f3e976d557c1d","tid":2022234,"uid":82070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9209819e0c5a3f80b28475ca1c1d37b7876eafbd","tid":2022234,"uid":29153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T08:09:38.000Z","msg":"無睇好耐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:12:05.000Z","msg":"心情有無好左?"},"citedBy":0,"repl